snippet.title: Battle Worlds: Kronos GC 2013 Trailer
snippet.description:
Battle Worlds: Kronos is a Kickstarter financed turn-based strategy game. This is a little trailer we made for GamesCom 2013 in Cologne.
Our web-site: http://www.battle-worlds.com
